                <h1 id="esoteric-dissonant-cycles-a-deep-dive">Esoteric &amp; Dissonant Cycles: A Deep Dive</h1>
<p>While the most common magical <a href="/w/magic-system/core-mechanics/cycles">Cycles</a> are built upon the transformational arts of the <a href="/w/magic-system/paths/the-22-paths">22 Arcana</a>, there exist a number of rare, theoretical, and often heretical Cycles. These are not tied to a specific Arcanum, but instead bridge fundamental concepts in novel ways, often with high Dissonance.</p>
<p>Mastery of these Cycles is the hallmark of the most specialized and dangerous mages in the world. They represent a "deep dive" into the fundamental physics of the Great System, often exploiting loopholes or creating paradoxes to achieve their potent effects. This document catalogues these known esoteric engines.</p>
<hr />
<h2 id="summary-of-esoteric-cycles">Summary of Esoteric Cycles</h2>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Cycle Name</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Sustained Effect</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="#c23-the-civic-heart-dissonant-2-node-loop-s4-s8">The Civic Heart</a></td>
<td>Dissonant 2-Node</td>
<td>An "Aura of Civic Harmony."</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="#c24-the-gamblers-forge-dissonant-2-node-loop-s2-s10">The Gambler's Forge</a></td>
<td>Dissonant 2-Node</td>
<td>An "Aura of Improbability Made Manifest."</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="#c25-the-war-dance-cadence-dissonant-2-node-loop-s3-s7">The War-Dance Cadence</a></td>
